TextEng: At least tell me about the fighters.
What do you know about Claudus?
Go away, kid, you bother me.
What do you know about the fighters?
You watch a lot of the fights. Are they fair?
Text: 경기를 많이 보는 것 같은데. 공정해?

TextEng: Is fights fair? You seem to know stuff.
Text: 싸움 공정해? 너 잘 아는 듯한데.

TextEng: And Third Round? Whats about that?
